共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後大家要幫手簽個聯署支持BNO平權救手足</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtcLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=30416e6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"e62c7c74f88f02f262c730ef6bcb8273ea36e3bb","tid":2032651,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:46:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/05/24/uBG76f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F05%2F24%2FuBG76f.gif&h=0095d262&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3b88df5e8b1abf3b09cd44becab408747fa6f50","tid":2032651,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:59:03.000Z","msg":"紅燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?射爆你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}